{"tid":748994,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)猛火爆1-2","createTime":"2018-07-19T15:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T18:44:45.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4d54e984c1d49544075ee72b9a4af4a47e080f92","tid":748994,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:47:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=pz9xdHpEethfkhPBdAN2QMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=23c28c9d\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=pz9xdHpEethfkhPBdAN2QMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b5fdc104\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=pz9xdHpEethfkhPBdAN2QMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=d8c6da99\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c4/猛火爆.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc4%2F%E7%8C%9B%E7%81%AB%E7%88%86.jpg&h=652b211c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9e/RED_2_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9e%2FRED_2_poster.jpg&h=fa1b39df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.法蘭克莫西斯（Frank Moses；布魯斯&middot;威利飾演）是一名自CIA退休的前特工，被CIA的分類為RED，即為已退休而極度危險的（Retired, Extremely Dangerous），他感到退休生活十分無趣沒有變化，唯一的樂趣是每月撕毀養老金支票藉故與養老金管理人莎拉羅斯（Sarah Ross；瑪莉&middot;露易絲&middot;派克飾演）在電話裡的談天說地時間，且法蘭克對莎拉在心中漸生情愫；一日法蘭克家中突然闖入了數名傭兵，想要將法蘭克滅口，法蘭克憑著過去的矯健身手將傭兵團擊退後，發現攻擊的背後有著巨大的陰謀存在；因此為了保護所愛的人，法蘭克決定召集過去的老戰友們，來對抗陰謀的幕後黑手並揭發真相&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2.出生入死、爾虞我詐的諜報世界裡，你要相信薑是老的辣！退而不休，寶刀未老的探員法蘭克（布魯斯威利 飾）憑著往昔經驗和過人能耐，將與他的昔日戰友再度出手，不但要拯救世界免於核子威脅，更要保全他們自己的老命...<br />\n<br />\n12 10AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=pz9xdHpEethfkhPBdAN2QMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c613c191\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=pz9xdHpEethfkhPBdAN2QMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=702abb2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f8a2e614937d12e97e04ecba6979ef22ec8c81","tid":748994,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522b5cf4dd5c34161680e2704b635a92a054989c","tid":748994,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T16:20:06.000Z","msg":"<